# Repository-wide environment variables. Per-app .env files override these:
#   apps/backend/.env.example   (ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, OPENAI_API_KEY, CORS_ORIGINS, HOST, PORT, WEB_CONCURRENCY)
#   apps/frontend/.env.example  (VITE_API_URL)
# Local dev: ./scripts/dev.sh (offset ports; exports CORS_ORIGINS + NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL automatically).
